Digital Image, Created February 2022. 

A lower resolution version of this image is currently in the teia logo rotation. 

One of my "turbulent determinism" style logos created recently for the teia logo submission form. Shared in anticipation of 700,000 OBJKTs minted.  

This artwork was created procedurally in Photoshop using custom macros and scripts, and was generated using the process shown in OBJKT 697827.
